newsitem.title: USA: RESEARCH ALERT - Fannie Mae cut by DMG.
newsitem.headline: RESEARCH ALERT - Fannie Mae cut by DMG.

text.p: Deutsche Morgan Grenfell said it downgraded Fannie Mae to accumulate from buy.
-- On Thursday, Fannie Mae posted second quarter earnings of $0.69 a share, up from $0.61 a share last year.
